# d38shop — frontend environment template
# Copy to frontend/.env on the server (optional). Do not commit real values.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Node
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
NODE_ENV=production

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Backend API URL (for server-side rendering / API client)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# When the frontend runs on the same host as the backend (Nginx proxies /api), the browser
# uses same-origin /api. For SSR (e.g. getProduct on the server), the frontend needs the
# backend base URL. Use API_URL (server-only) or NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL (exposed to client).
# Examples: http://127.0.0.1:3001 (dev), https://your-domain.com (production same host).
API_URL=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=
